version_description:
Commanders!
Announcing "Honor and Vengeance," our exciting New Feature!
*New & addictive PvP Faction gameplay
*New gameplay system that rewards strong guild teamwork & competition
*Earn Vengeance points by eliminating & avenging the opposing guild members
*All-new class of Vengeance weapons for PvP warfare
*Collect, earn & level up Vengeance weapons to deal even more damage
*New individual & team bonuses
In this update, we've made the following changes.
* Fixed World Domination crash issues
